metadata.name: Antiheroes
metadata.description:
Sometimes all this racing with FOMO gets tiresome, and you want a little rest. What could be better than to get together with friends and have a great time? Who knows what we came up with there? After all, friendship is magic. Dark, evil magic. Heh heh.

P.S. Why do we need swords? Never mind, we just like swords.
